title: About
text: Hello, My name is Jackson Hamlin and I am a third year student at UNL. I am double majoring in Sports Media/Communication and PGA Golf Management. I’ve been a sports fan my whole life, but I tend to lean heavily on the golf side, and yes, I did say golf was a sport. Not a hobby here. Enjoy the site!
